<div style="width:300px">



<center><h1>Water mediated hydrogen bonds</font></h1></center>

<font color="blue">LeView</font> allows the user to display  possible water-mediated interactions involving the ligand or ion. By clicking on the <b>"Water Mediated"</b> menu, all the possible water-mediated hydrogen bonds are displayed (limited to four H2O). Click on one of them to display it on the diagram and click on again to hide it.


